To get the alarm working,

First, write to file alarm.sh, rtcwake -m mem --local --date


Receive input to indicate if the alarm should be today, or tomorrow.

	if today, append the date today.
	else append the date today + day 1.

Receive input to indicate hour.
Append to file "HOUR:"

Receive input to indicate minute.
Append to file "MIN".

Append "echo Success"

